															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610250363" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;" >A Random Day</a></span> <span class="odate time_1455507807 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">15 Feb 2016 03:43</span>
