			<div class="content" id="post-content-2457308">
									

<p>Part 1 of a series.</p>
<p>Thanks to my teammates GreenWolf, sirpudding, and TyGently for helping me brainstorm this tale and providing feedback and support. Thanks to MrWrong, WrongJohnSilver, Faminepulse, Lazar Lyusternik, and everyone else in chat for their feedback.</p>
<p>THE SEQUELS:</p>
<p>1. Avatara<br />
2. <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/grant-request-for-investigating-the-potential-application-of">GRANT REQUEST FOR INVESTIGATING THE APPLICATION OF CERTAIN RESEARCH ASSETS IN OVERCOMING INHERENT LIMITATIONS OF THE HUMAN BODY</a><br />
3. <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-2970">SCP-2970 (Holy Misplacement)</a><br />
4. <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/operation-azure-peregrine">Operation AZURE PEREGRINE</a><br />
5. <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/the-lord-of-endowments">The Lord of Endowments</a><br />
6. <a href="/samsara">Samsara</a></p>
<p>See more of my work on my <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-arvind-desais-personnel-file">author page</a>!</p>

