<p>A cautious upvote for now. I'm interested enough to wait for the next part. I do wonder how much of the body horror was necessary. Seemed a tad excessive. But I do like the idea of mutants doing dirty work. Reminds me of the Nurgle mythos but in a good way. Keep it up.</p>
<p>Edit: After a second read, I think the body horror is well justified and not just there for shock value. Still looking forward to more.</p>

